---
<section id="work" class="case-section">
  <div class="case-inner container">
    <div style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
      <div class="section-tag">Client Work</div>
      <h2 class="section-heading">From invisible to <span class="accent">in-demand.</span></h2>
    </div>

    <div class="case-card">
      <div class="case-left">
        <span class="case-badge">Active Retainer — Law Firm</span>
        <h3>Targeting diaspora clients who wouldn't have found them otherwise</h3>
        <p>
          A Nairobi-based law firm serving Kenyans living abroad had no functional web presence —
          an outdated site, no Google Business Profile, and zero content. Their target clients
          were searching from the UK, US, and Canada and finding competitors instead.
        </p>
        <br/>
        <p>
          We rebuilt their site from scratch, activated and optimised their GBP,
          and launched a monthly content plan targeting diaspora search terms.
          Within 30 days, they had their first inbound inquiry from the UK through organic search.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="case-right">
        <div class="case-metric">
          <span class="case-metric-label">Time to first result</span>
          <span class="case-metric-value">30 <span class="metric-span">days</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="case-metric">
          <span class="case-metric-label">Channels activated</span>
          <span class="case-metric-value">4 <span class="metric-span">channels</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="case-metric">
          <span class="case-metric-label">Content pieces / month</span>
          <span class="case-metric-value">8 <span class="metric-span">pieces</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="case-metric">
          <span class="case-metric-label">Retainer type</span>
          <span class="case-metric-value metric-special">Monthly</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
